# Guard against accidental nested duplicate of the repository tree under src/.
# A previous regression committed an entire copy of the repo to src/sdk-python/,
# which broke mypy with a "Duplicate module named 'strands'" error. Ignore that
# path so the same accident cannot re-enter the working tree silently.
/src/sdk-python/
